{"type":"message","id":"8608594b","parentId":"8094dfc6","timestamp":"2026-02-15T12:07:29.957Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Contemplating the Code**\n\nI'm thinking about the user's request to revamp the Telegram menu for their \"DMarket HFT\" bot. I've noted that `openclaw.json` is absent, which might be a critical config file. Also, the core script, `src/main.py`, is just a basic loop. I'm now mulling over how to transform it into the Telegram bot implementation.\n\n\n**Considering the Bot's Structure**\n\nI'm starting to formulate the bot's architecture. The initial plan involved using `src/main.py` to handle Telegram commands and interact with `agent_wrapper.py`. Now, I'm focusing on the Telegram bot's core structure. I need to integrate the `python-telegram-bot` library, assuming it is installed, and then define the necessary commands: `/dm_start` and `/dm_stop`. Currently, I'm examining the role of `agent_wrapper.py`.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1771157249954_555","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"dir src"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":5996,"output":356,"cacheRead":4935,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":6352,"cost":{"input":0.011992,"output":0.004272,"cacheRead":0.000987,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.017251000000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771157243570}}
{"type":"message","id":"fb33a930","parentId":"8608594b","timestamp":"2026-02-15T12:07:30.138Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec_1771157249954_555","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"��⠫��: C:\\Users\\west2\\.openclaw\\workspace\\src\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----        14.02.2026     12:04                core                                                                 \r\nd-----        15.02.2026     13:35                __pycache__                                                          \r\n-a----        15.02.2026     14:02           4075 agent_wrapper.py                                                     \r\n-a----        15.02.2026     13:34           2876 deploy_safety.py                                                     \r\n-a----        15.02.2026     14:01            579 main.py                                                              \r\n-a----        15.02.2026     13:19           2346 stress_test.py"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":179,"aggregated":"��⠫��: C:\\Users\\west2\\.openclaw\\workspace\\src\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----        14.02.2026     12:04                core                                                                 \r\nd-----        15.02.2026     13:35                __pycache__                                                          \r\n-a----        15.02.2026     14:02           4075 agent_wrapper.py                                                     \r\n-a----        15.02.2026     13:34      